{"tid":608061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【瘋狂科學家】為證「百毒不侵」 科學家任毒蛇咬","createTime":"2018-03-28T00:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T01:40:33.000Z","uid":122,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"54825a79509bf9ec86185d8415cb5b48adea0b09","tid":608061,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:20:40.000Z","msg":"美國一名業餘科學家為研製萬能抗蛇毒血清，不惜任世界十大毒蛇之一咬自己，勇氣和專業精神可嘉。<br />\n<br />\n聲稱身體能抗蛇毒的弗里德（Tim Friede）以身試毒，有意無意讓一條黑曼巴蛇在手指和手臂咬了四口，並拍片為證。<br />\n<br />\n被黑曼巴蛇咬傷，通常在15分鐘內毒發身亡，但片段中的弗里德，雖然傷口流血，卻若無其事。<br />\n<br />\n研究自體免疫17年的弗里德，被其毒無比的蛇咬過不下200次，試過被眼鏡蛇咬到昏迷，差點喪命。他希望通過這些「實驗」，有朝一日研發出可以救命　的抗蛇毒疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n弗里德為研究不僅差點犧牲性命，還失去婚姻：妻子結婚20年後再無法忍受他對蛇多過對她，2016年與他離婚。<br />\n<br />\n或許有人覺得弗里德傻，但大無畏精神至少得到加州大學微生物學博士漢利（Dr Brian Hanley）欣賞。他希望通過他創辦的基因療法公司，幫助弗里德研發疫苗及尋找投資者。<br />\n<br />\n之後會變superhero 定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f76f56db6ffa8de3aa598c18be5e40e04f5e76","tid":608061,"uid":82317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:25:09.000Z","msg":"好似話佢咁多年無病過"},{"pid":"566467d86c29f47b536dc221d4d9fb68b3183ff5","tid":608061,"uid":67903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:30:52.000Z","msg":"Voldemort"},{"pid":"c468bfc24d1be4127b067854d0c11a58a3bcd9b0","tid":608061,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:32:03.000Z","msg":"蛇俠"},{"pid":"7b3e734f0eebfba064bea6efa101242f4f67e0c5","tid":608061,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c25f47245856cc372ec519662d9c6d9efbd346","tid":608061,"uid":30120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:41:57.000Z","msg":"百毒不侵既毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a804d9a8f25466e9798aefe1ab7bb157879e58c3","tid":608061,"uid":1880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:42:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似話佢咁多年無病過</blockquote><br />\nunbreakable <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1249c64d86905ee7c1cf73d2a4f881c3275c007b","tid":608061,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"佢d血咪好值錢"}]}